snippet.textDisplay:
Both Aima & Sahir  are Superb.

Saraiki dialect is at it's best in this song.

Love the Song & want to say this.

Let India  &  Pakistan remain  separate but live  as Brotherly Nations.

Always Wish for both Nations to Grow leaps & bounds in each n every Field.

But Let's Honestly Respect the the Rich culture , Music, Traditions ,Tribes, linguistics, Festivals & genuine Desi ness of each other for ever.

Lets expel  all enemity amongst us to Achieve everlasting peace.

Also Hope the politicians at both sides  Realise the Fact that we were  one Nation through out our entire history & arrive at terms of Non-War treaty  for the development & prosperity of the indian sub continent.
